# Project: {{PROJECT_NAME}}

## Overview

This is a **headless ExpressionEngine (Coilpack) + Next.js** project. ExpressionEngine with Coilpack (Laravel integration) serves as the backend CMS with API routes, and Next.js provides the frontend (React SSR/SSG).

- **Backend URL**: {{DDEV_PRIMARY_URL}}
- **Control Panel**: {{DDEV_PRIMARY_URL}}/eecp
- **Frontend URL**: http://localhost:3000
- **Environment**: DDEV (backend) + Node.js (frontend)

**Coilpack Documentation**: https://expressionengine.github.io/coilpack-docs/

## Tech Stack

### Backend (ExpressionEngine + Coilpack)
- **CMS**: ExpressionEngine 7.x + Coilpack
- **Framework**: Laravel 10.x
- **API**: Laravel API routes (REST) + optional GraphQL
- **PHP Version**: {{DDEV_PHP}}
- **Database**: {{DDEV_DB_TYPE}}/{{DDEV_DB_VERSION}}
- **Environment**: DDEV (Docker-based local dev)

### Frontend (Next.js)
- **Framework**: Next.js 14+ (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Data Fetching**: React Server Components + REST/GraphQL
- **UI**: Headless UI / Radix

