## Development Commands

### Backend (Coilpack via DDEV)
```bash
ddev start                         # Start DDEV containers
ddev stop                          # Stop DDEV containers
ddev ssh                           # Access container shell
ddev describe                      # Show project info

# Laravel Artisan
ddev artisan route:list            # List all routes (including API)
ddev artisan cache:clear           # Clear Laravel cache
ddev artisan optimize:clear        # Clear all caches

# ExpressionEngine CLI
ddev ee cache:clear                # Clear all EE caches
ddev ee list                       # List all EE commands

# Frontend Build (for any backend-served assets)
ddev npm install
ddev npm run dev
ddev npm run build
```

